{"tid":26293,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"酒樓蒸魚好食 有咩秘訣","createTime":"2016-12-06T15:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T04:33:57.000Z","uid":40684,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fee1ae75e451dfe39f5d5f2da9901b24a9e44e4e","tid":26293,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"去親酒樓食都覺得d蒸魚好正<br />\n又滑又好食<br />\n其實有咩秘訣先蒸到一條好魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0de34930da11b176e3b87d8ab304a1355275211","tid":26293,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去親酒樓食都覺得d蒸魚好正<br />\n又滑又好食<br />\n其實有咩秘訣先蒸到一條好魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n花生油，魚露（靚既），唔好蒸太熟<br />\n蔥油一定要滾起淋"},{"pid":"d704a1971b6064b5340e7f637e37ccf39ad5c17a","tid":26293,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去親酒樓食都覺得d蒸魚好正<br />\n又滑又好食<br />\n其實有咩秘訣先蒸到一條好魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n花生油，魚露（靚既），唔好蒸太熟<br />\n蔥油一定要滾起淋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n花生油 魚露要落大約幾多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7aaff4863736090dbfd8e205b138e0b0026808a","tid":26293,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:07:10.000Z","msg":"人地個蒸爐好撚大架，屋企係做唔到既"},{"pid":"fe8a4bea7b2937bc28d5ea8fb1c4ed5be5e41cea","tid":26293,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:18:24.000Z","msg":"有啲酒樓啲魚係烚到半熟 再蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屋企蒸可以揾野 撐高魚身 匙羹 筷子 蔥都得<br />\n蒸果啲水要貼碟底 蒸完倒走碟啲水 落蔥 滾油 豉油"},{"pid":"1dd5cb890ed9bd48dffb34ad0d4a8c08bf2f5c93","tid":26293,"uid":53769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:03:18.000Z","msg":"酒樓個蒸爐大力過家用爐 好難整到一樣"},{"pid":"8c8956fa407937019c4517897a2177f85dcf917e","tid":26293,"uid":53292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:11:16.000Z","msg":"其實重點除左隔水蒸之外 係時間同火侯問題 火應該中火同大火之間 時間一定要短 寧願熄火焗一焗 大約一斤既魚 唔好蒸多過10分鐘"},{"pid":"25574c5212f86179a2b5a38e876cf019a51ae6cc","tid":26293,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T22:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去親酒樓食都覺得d蒸魚好正<br />\n又滑又好食<br />\n其實有咩秘訣先蒸到一條好魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n花生油，魚露（靚既），唔好蒸太熟<br />\n蔥油一定要滾起淋</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n花生油 魚露要落大約幾多到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蒸魚一定係隔水大火蒸，隻碟放條魚上去一定要乾水<br />\n睇你蒸咩魚，厚身定薄身，有無落過雪櫃，冬天同夏天，一條一斤重既魚，d班之類又放過落雪櫃，我會10分鐘，前提係冬天加放過落雪櫃，夏天減DD， 無放雪櫃蒸少一分鐘"},{"pid":"c95e5eee9b57ace8ecf1bd545d2d2250dc1a56f8","tid":26293,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:04:34.000Z","msg":"我想知酒樓d蒸魚豉油點溝多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次食蒸魚都要點好多豉油夾蔥絲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de73dae34f81f384b8a975257a10dc723d17dc27","tid":26293,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:10:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想知酒樓d蒸魚豉油點溝多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次食蒸魚都要點好多豉油夾蔥絲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪話豉油，花生油，魚露，少少，少少糖"},{"pid":"b0ed2ee7cc74fa9867437418d26c4653f8f817c5","tid":26293,"uid":6677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:13:21.000Z","msg":"上youtube聽吓廚房佬rap就知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2121f71c7a827a7b96909c84aafd9e7dd98ab7","tid":26293,"uid":2272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:20:25.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"69393f39df6d5948bae3a5ba28b5b2e4508c83a2","tid":26293,"uid":36278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想知酒樓d蒸魚豉油點溝多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次食蒸魚都要點好多豉油夾蔥絲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪話豉油，花生油，魚露，少少，少少糖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蒸魚不嬲都係油另外煮，6-8茶匙花生油，起鍋，油滾爆香薑蔥，再放豉油，好少好少糖，同幾滴魚露"},{"pid":"ade9e1d4ac9c8f2359a63ee51a0645e6e4982779","tid":26293,"uid":22505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:28:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想知酒樓d蒸魚豉油點溝多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次食蒸魚都要點好多豉油夾蔥絲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪話豉油，花生油，魚露，少少，少少糖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蒸魚不嬲都係油另外煮，6-8茶匙花生油，起鍋，油滾爆香薑蔥，再放豉油，好少好少糖，同幾滴魚露</blockquote><br />\n揾日試下整先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2bb08196c25e853bcfe283f5551cb49d462e75","tid":26293,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想知酒樓d蒸魚豉油點溝多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次食蒸魚都要點好多豉油夾蔥絲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪話豉油，花生油，魚露，少少，少少糖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蒸魚不嬲都係油另外煮，6-8茶匙花生油，起鍋，油滾爆香薑蔥，再放豉油，好少好少糖，同幾滴魚露</blockquote><br />\n揾日試下整先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n生油老抽魚露搞開先，試左味佢先落，驚你新仔重手"},{"pid":"4ce225a0d2b8ce9cd8ee12f6da5a8e0c2a8adfc6","tid":26293,"uid":2858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:37:59.000Z","msg":"聽講淋面嗰啲係豬油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起都肚餓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6196c0872e7b99102057fe2ea23f84836e0a6738","tid":26293,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:43:45.000Z","msg":"已經唔記得係唔係要加甜醋定糖醋<br />\n早幾年有去人地度食飯<br />\n佢就係煮到酒樓蒸魚果種味道<br />\n果條魚雖然係好普通.但果種味道真係難忘"},{"pid":"2ad79bfacf6354be441ec47518b68f70200a8b3f","tid":26293,"uid":36278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:49:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講淋面嗰啲係豬油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起都肚餓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n豬油個d 又係一絕，花生油都係，<br />\n芥花子油就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394f2deacec32ab1a4099b4037dcf9bb93e2427a","tid":26293,"uid":6090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:49:30.000Z","msg":"其實有時覺得酒樓蒸魚好睇彩數，一時就鞋到仆街，有時就還可以，如果識個經理咪好啲囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我阿嫲係屋企用大鍋黎蒸都好好味又滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b9236eb6b795f21f2e59e9f0fdbb918e9e3679","tid":26293,"uid":37581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T23:55:47.000Z","msg":"酒樓蒸樓用蒸櫃蒸 蒸氣力猛個屋企好多 <br />\n蒸魚豉油 離不開萬字醬油（生抽）美極 魚露 雞粉 冰糖 芫茜 老抽 水<br />\n蒸起落蔥絲 贊熱熟油"},{"pid":"9e6a4ceeca47d3229d6986af534c0faa48f8e190","tid":26293,"uid":37581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T00:03:24.000Z","msg":"如果你叫果條魚貴會塞雞油同搽少少海鹽蒸 會蒸到緊緊熟或少少生再贊油比佢岩岩好<br />\n贊既熟油會煉過 用薑同蔥浸到乾哂出哂香味<br />\n利申 從事中式廚房多年 米芝蓮食府 酒樓 茶記都跑過"},{"pid":"f9070782f70fff052b46c0efda735415f79afd80","tid":26293,"uid":58606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T00:10:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c841f3c9ea2e6c522cb5bed1db849de3698c6f64","tid":26293,"uid":49657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T00:25:20.000Z","msg":"我見啲師傅會放舊雞既肥膏係魚面<br />\n同埋用筷子long起先蒸"},{"pid":"8a51062877af17a32928ab3c1bef9d73eb6f3d95","tid":26293,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T00:31:31.000Z","msg":"上面話酒樓蒸爐勁嗰啲，有幾多個用過家用蒸爐?咪又係用鑊蒸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平平地惠而佬蒸爐已經蒸得好靚啦"},{"pid":"fec01b9855cf1f80cc91e3805d17b732cbcfbbd0","tid":26293,"uid":5601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T00:33:01.000Z","msg":"d豉油撈飯超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}